- That's a big 10-4.

936
01:24:23,631 --> 01:24:26,384
Damn, he's been stirring up some trouble.

937
01:24:35,310 --> 01:24:38,021
Ooh, it's the Bandit!

938
01:24:53,995 --> 01:24:58,958
I'm Hot To Trot. Just tell me how
I can help and I'm with ya, body and soul.

939
01:24:59,125 --> 01:25:02,420
- Channel clear.
- Breaker one-nine, breaker one-nine.

940
01:25:02,587 --> 01:25:04,839
Is that Hot Pants Hilliard
yakkin' out there?

941
01:25:05,006 --> 01:25:08,009
- And who wants to know?
- This is the Bandit, darling.

942
01:25:08,176 --> 01:25:11,846
Well, where are you,
you bodied-up, smooth-talkin' thing?

943
01:25:12,013 --> 01:25:14,224
And how can I help?
Bring it back.

944
01:25:14,391 --> 01:25:17,310
You still workin' at that
choke-and-puke on West 85?

945
01:25:17,477 --> 01:25:21,022
Affirmative, affirmative.
I'm still dishin' it out.

946
01:25:21,564 --> 01:25:26,236
We'll come screamin' by in five minutes
