947
01:25:26,861 --> 01:25:29,489
How 'bout gettin' those pallies
of yours out there, block 'em off?

948
01:25:29,656 --> 01:25:32,659
Love to! But hey,
you're gonna owe me one.

949
01:25:32,826 --> 01:25:36,538
- I owe you a big one.
- That's a big 10-4.

950
01:25:36,705 --> 01:25:38,373
10-4.

951
01:25:40,208 --> 01:25:44,421
All right gang, we're gonna go
for a big smokey red 22. Wahoo!

952
01:25:44,587 --> 01:25:46,381
- Ride with me?
- Yeah.

953
01:25:52,178 --> 01:25:57,350
- You sure we ain't gonna get in trouble?
- Nah. I've done it before.

954
01:26:12,073 --> 01:26:16,036
- We're comin' at you, darlin'. Are you ready?
- Ready, willin' and able.

955
01:26:16,202 --> 01:26:20,290
"Ready and willing." Ha.
She always was.

956
01:26:23,543 --> 01:26:27,130
OK, gang, be alert,
'cause here he comes.

957
01:26:27,297 --> 01:26:31,885
- Well, go ahead and answer.
- 10-4, Hot Pants. We copy.

958
01:26:32,052 --> 01:26:34,012
Let go of the button.

959
01:27:16,513 --> 01:27:20,725
Paydirt. I just picked up
the Bandit eastbound on 95.

960
01:27:20,892 --> 01:27:22,477
All units converge.

961
01:27:22,644 --> 01:27:26,106
I copy, Chopper One.
I'm on my way.

962
01:27:39,160 --> 01:27:40,370
Heading for the fairgrounds!

963
01:28:04,436 --> 01:28:08,440
This is car 12, Bobby Lee,
and I have him westbound on 75.
