- Four miles. Goddamn it!
- Four miles...

966
01:28:37,218 --> 01:28:40,764
Bo, did you count on this?

967
01:28:40,930 --> 01:28:43,641
I mean, all of this?

968
01:28:48,646 --> 01:28:51,566
No, I didn't, honey.

969
01:28:55,737 --> 01:28:59,157
- Cledus?
- Talk to me, my boy.

970
01:28:59,324 --> 01:29:02,869
Goddamn it, son,
