Hot damn, we're gonna make it.

980
01:30:05,557 --> 01:30:08,393
Move them vehicles.
We gotta get through!

981
01:30:08,560 --> 01:30:10,979
Here they come!

982
01:30:48,308 --> 01:30:52,020
Daddy, you're about to have
your evenin' ruined for you.

983
01:31:06,826 --> 01:31:08,870
- OK.
- All right.

984
